TODO list items/groups are structured into a tree-like graph, with each node holding the following

ID: some id that is used to uniquely identify a list item/group
Title: a string that specifies a title for the item/group
Description: a string that specifies a larger body of text describing the item or group
Parents: a list of ids that specify the ids of the parents of the node
Children: a list of ids that specify the ids of the children of the node
Username: a string that provides some kind of identifier for who should be able access the data contained within the node
Metadata: json string that can store arbitrary data for any future additions to functionality
